Exp4 : DML COMMAND- UPDATE


1. Update the price of a particular product.

mysql> update product set price=25 where pid=404;
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.04 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

mysql> select *from product;
+-----+--------------+---------+
| pid | pname        | price   |
+-----+--------------+---------+
| 404 | milk         |   25.00 |
| 408 | pringles     |  100.00 |
| 409 | sauce        |   70.00 |
| 411 | nonstick pan |  700.00 |
| 414 | maggi        |  150.00 |
| 423 | cooker       | 1700.00 |
| 448 | pen          |   10.00 |
+-----+--------------+---------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


2. Change the name of city ‘calicut’ to ‘kozhikode’ in the customer table.

mysql> update customer set city='kozhikode' where city='calicut';
Query OK, 3 rows affected (0.46 sec)
Rows matched: 3  Changed: 3  Warnings: 0

mysql> select *from product;
+-----+--------------+---------+
| pid | pname        | price   |
+-----+--------------+---------+
| 404 | milk         |   25.00 |
| 408 | pringles     |  100.00 |
| 409 | sauce        |   70.00 |
| 411 | nonstick pan |  700.00 |
| 414 | maggi        |  150.00 |
| 423 | cooker       | 1700.00 |
| 448 | pen          |   10.00 |
+-----+--------------+---------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Update all prices with 2% of its original price.


mysql> update product set price=price+(.02*100);
Query OK, 7 rows affected (0.06 sec)
Rows matched: 7  Changed: 7  Warnings: 0

mysql> select *from product;
+-----+--------------+---------+
| pid | pname        | price   |
+-----+--------------+---------+
| 404 | milk         |   27.00 |
| 408 | pringles     |  102.00 |
| 409 | sauce        |   72.00 |
| 411 | nonstick pan |  702.00 |
| 414 | maggi        |  152.00 |
| 423 | cooker       | 1702.00 |
| 448 | pen          |   12.00 |
+-----+--------------+---------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. Change the address, city, phone number of a particular customer.

mysql> update customer set city='goa',address='puthiyaveettil',ph_no=8787965432 where id=110;
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.05 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

mysql> select *from customer;
+-----+-----------+----------------+-----------+------------+
| id  | name      | address        | city      | ph_no      |
